( also spelled Vijnanabhikshu ) was a Hindu philosopher from Bihar , variously dated to the 15th or 16th century , [ 1 ] [ 2 ] known for his commentary on various schools of Hindu philosophy , particularly the Yoga text of Patanjali . [ 3 ] [ 4 ]
